OL,3,CAssisted dying could be fully
OL,4,Clegalised in Jersey by 2027
OL,6,FLandmark draft legislation published
OL,7,Fin Jersey could see the island
OL,8,Flegalise assisted dying by 2027.
OL,10,FThe final proposals, put forward by
OL,11,Fthe Council of Ministers, follow the
OL,12,FStates' historic decision last year to
OL,13,Fallow people who have a terminal
OL,14,Fillness to end their lives with the
OL,15,Fhelp of medical professionals.
OL,17,FThey provide a detailed framework
OL,18,Fwhich outlines the strict conditions
OL,19,Fand safeguards under which residents
OL,20,Fwould be able to make this choice.
