OL,6,FThe full proposals outline further
OL,7,Fdetail - including conditions under
OL,8,Fwhich requests will be refused, how to
OL,9,Fwithdraw requests or pause the
OL,10,Fprocess, the writing of care plans,
OL,11,Fand the need for witnesses at the
OL,12,Fcarrying out of the assisted death.
OL,14,FThe draft law also describes the right
OL,15,Fto refuse to participate in assisted
OL,16,Fdying for any reason.
