OL,4,Clegalised in Jersey by 2027
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man became the first place
OL,7,Fin the British Isles to pass their
OL,8,Fequivalent legislation in March, and
OL,9,Fare looking to introduce the system in
OL,10,Fearly 2027.
OL,12,FPoliticians in Westminster recently
OL,13,Fpassed the next stage of their
OL,14,Fassisted dying bill covering England
OL,15,Fand Wales.
OL,17,FThe States of Guernsey rejected
OL,18,Fproposals in 2018, but recent calls
OL,19,Fhave been made to revisit the issue.
