OL,3,CAssisted dying could be fully
OL,4,Clegalised in Jersey by 2027
OL,6,FIf approved in November, there will be
OL,7,Fan 18-month implementation period -
OL,8,Fduring which the assisted dying
OL,9,Fservice will be set up, healthcare
OL,10,Fprofessionals trained, and further
OL,11,Fpublic information sessions will take
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,FThis phase will be overseen by a
OL,15,Fdesignated Assisted Dying Assurance
OL,16,Fand Delivery Committee.
OL,18,FThe law would then come into effect in
OL,19,F2027.
